I"q<p><strong>Medium humanoid (lizardfolk), neutral</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 13 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 27 (5d8+5)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft., swim 30 ft.</p>

